#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.365"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.10:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu viharati aññatarasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Kosalans in a certain "
"forest grove."

msgctxt "sn7.10:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena aññatarassa bhāradvājagottassa brāhmaṇassa catuddasa "
"balībaddā naṭṭhā honti."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time one of the brahmins of the Bhāradvāja clan had lost "
"fourteen oxen."

msgctxt "sn7.10:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhāradvājagotto brāhmaṇo te balībadde gavesanto yena so vanasaṇḍo "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā addasa bhagavantaṃ tasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe nisinnaṃ "
"pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāya parimukhaṃ satiṃ upaṭṭhapetvā."
msgstr ""
"While looking for them he went to that forest, where he saw the Buddha "
"sitting down cross-legged, with his body straight, and mindfulness "
"established right there."

msgctxt "sn7.10:1.4"
msgid ""
"Disvāna yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato santike imā "
"gāthāyo abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"He went up to the Buddha, and recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence:"

