#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.10:16.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhāradvājagotto brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he had spoken, the brahmin said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn7.10:16.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama."
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! …"

msgctxt "sn7.10:16.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā "
"vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya:"
" ‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evameva bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena "
"dhammo pakāsito."
msgstr ""
"As if he were righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing "
"out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark so people with good "
"eyes can see what’s there, Master Gotama has made the teaching clear in many "
"ways."

msgctxt "sn7.10:16.4"
msgid "Esāhaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca."
msgstr ""
"I go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the teaching, and to the mendicant "
"Saṅgha."

msgctxt "sn7.10:16.5"
msgid ""
"Labheyyāhaṃ bhoto gotamassa santike pabbajjaṃ, labheyyaṃ upasampadan”ti."
msgstr ""
"Sir, may I receive the going forth, the ordination in the Buddha’s presence?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "sn7.10:17.1"
msgid ""
"Alattha kho bhāradvājagotto brāhmaṇo bhagavato santike pabbajjaṃ, alattha "
"upasampadaṃ."
msgstr ""
"And the brahmin received the going forth, the ordination in the Buddha’s "
"presence."

msgctxt "sn7.10:17.2"
msgid ""
"Acirūpasampanno panāyasmā bhāradvājo eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī "
"pahitatto viharanto nacirasseva—yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā "
"anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme "
"sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihāsi."
msgstr ""
"Not long after his ordination, Venerable Bhāradvāja, living alone, "
"withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute, soon realized the supreme end of "
"the spiritual path in this very life. He lived having achieved with his own "
"insight the goal for which people from good families rightly go forth from "
"the lay life to homelessness."

msgctxt "sn7.10:17.3"
msgid ""
"“Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā”ti "
"abbhaññāsi."
msgstr ""
"He understood: “Rebirth is ended; the spiritual journey has been completed; "
"what had to be done has been done; there is no return to any state of "
"existence.”"

msgctxt "sn7.10:17.4"
msgid "Aññataro ca panāyasmā bhāradvājo arahataṃ ahosīti."
msgstr "And Venerable Bhāradvāja became one of the perfected."

